```

```

---

### Comparison: Linear vs Branching Programming

| Basis | Linear Programming | Branching Programming |
|-------|-------------------|----------------------|
| **Propounder** | B.F. Skinner | Norman Crowder |
| **Response type** | Constructed (learner writes) | Multiple choice |
| **Frame size** | Small | Large |
| **Branching** | No branching | Multiple branches |
| **Error handling** | Prevent errors | Remedial instruction for errors |
| **Learner control** | Fixed sequence | Learner chooses path |
| **Reinforcement** | After each frame | Only at correct answers |
| **Theory basis** | Operant conditioning | Insight learning |
| **Interest level** | Less interesting | More interesting |

